When it beginneth therefore to shoot in this maner, they saie it is come, and then sorthwith they spread it abroad, first thicke‚ and afterward thinner and thinner vpon the said floore (as it commeth), and there it lieth by the space of one and twentie dayes at the least.’' B. ii. 0. 6.
